---
title: Sweet-Sticky Chicken & Pear Slaw with Garlic Couscous & Japanese Mayo
description: Sweetly glazed chicken bites are popping with flavour in a bowl that’s already got the aromas of garlic rice. If that still isn’t enough, a Japanese mayo may be the thing to tick all your tasty boxes. We’ll let you give it a try and find out.

*We’ve replaced the
jasmine rice with
couscous due to local
ingredient availability.
It’ll be just as delicious,
just follow your recipe!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65cc26553dbfdc1d2e0c556b-a990a9eb.jpeg
